docs.text: Home intro ... A quick run-down about me: I’m a proud Pythonista specializing in high-performance backend web services. Python 3, asyncio, and typing are my jam. I’m a science-fiction writer, currently working on a space opera set in a future where data is the only currency. I’m a lover of Shakespeare and classical text, and run a private group that gets together weekly all over NYC to read his works together.
